      <description>&lt;p&gt;This blog is about how I build my blog. The blog is built with Hugo and hosted in GitHub Pages.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;If you are interested in building your own site using Hugo and GitHub Pages, focus on the &lt;code&gt;Quick Start&lt;/code&gt; part. Follow the given references and you can make it.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Other parts are about my solutions to some problems or special requirements I faced when I built it.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 id=&#34;quick-start&#34;&gt;Quick Start&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Just follow &lt;a href=&#34;https://gohugo.io/getting-started/quick-start/&#34;&gt;Hugo - Quick Start&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a href=&#34;https://gohugo.io/hosting-and-deployment/hosting-on-github/&#34;&gt;Hugo - Host on GitHub&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
